sets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8f807a989fcf654649ba3a8ee0801ea48f43df","tid":35854,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔係得一幕好睇既<br />\n<br />\n友情之銀<br />\n<br />\n姆吉卡鑄劍<br />\n<br />\n殛克無雙+打魔導王<br />\n<br />\n兩個老豆隻抽<br />\n<br />\n龍人同火佬啲劇情都幾正</blockquote><br />\n凱爾.角萊利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初時主角仲懷疑佢係某奸角Boss 但其實只是撞名<br />\n係主角比群毆個陣突然好撚型咁出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冧樓幫仔擋石個度 細個睇好撚sad"},{"pid":"0d925af897358df0d6c7ba619f38212dd8de1f4d","tid":35854,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"每年起碼翻睇一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd13ed11a836194c626575a0919a6cfe6082bc0","tid":35854,"uid":8542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每年起碼翻睇一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cff3ff50808d13dd143540415c1948a4c82c9cc","tid":35854,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔係得一幕好睇既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">友情之銀</span><br />\n<br />\n姆吉卡鑄劍<br />\n<br />\n殛克無雙+打魔導王<br />\n<br />\n兩個老豆隻抽<br />\n<br />\n龍人同火佬啲劇情都幾正</blockquote><br />\n雷娜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b67effce4eabee94e180032827381e84e2650a","tid":35854,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每年起碼翻睇一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji